located: on a distant mountain, as with some natives of British New
Guinea;\[8\] or where the sun sets (compare Egyptian ideas); or on an
island far away;\[9\] or under the sea;\[10\] or in the heavens, either
in some defintitely designated luminary or in some indefinite locality
(Omahas regard the Milky Way as the path to this home by which spirits
pass in turn to and through seven spirit worlds).\[11\] At times the
information is quite definite, as for example in parts of New Guinea.

